      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEBLEC POLLY (1) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fifth (30.90) at Murray Bridge. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Has ability and looks hard to stop. TRUST DEED (7) goes very well here starting nine times for three wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (30.00) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. VOSS ALI (8) has been on speed at the last couple here and fought on to hit the frame, last start finishing third beaten 5.5 lengths (23.15). Suited by the extra trip here. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading chance. STARLIGHT JEWEL (5) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.",
